      "title": "Transcribe :CreatedBy wNum to :Dnode wNum",
      "text": "MATCH (d:Dnode)-[ee:CreatedBye]-\u003e(k:CreatedBy {wNum:0})\nSET d.wNum\u003dk.wNum\nRETURN d.wNum\n\nMATCH (d:Dnode)-[ee:CreatedBye]-\u003e(k:CreatedBy {wNum:1})\nSET d.wNum\u003dk.wNum\nRETURN d.wNum\n \nMATCH (d:Dnode)-[ee:CreatedBye]-\u003e(k:CreatedBy {wNum:2})\nSET d.wNum\u003dk.wNum\nRETURN d.wNum \n\nMATCH (d:Dnode)-[ee:CreatedBye]-\u003e(k:CreatedBy {wNum:3})\nSET d.wNum\u003dk.wNum\nRETURN d.wNum\n\nMATCH (d:Dnode)-[ee:CreatedBye]-\u003e(k:CreatedBy {wNum:4})\nSET d.wNum\u003dk.wNum\nRETURN d.wNum\n\nMATCH (d:Dnode)-[ee:CreatedBye]-\u003e(k:CreatedBy {wNum:5})\nSET d.wNum\u003dk.wNum\nRETURN d.wNum",
